VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'nice job with a lot of those color filters and the ability to customize those. And then if I want more creative control, yeah, I can bring the raw files in and I can play with them, edit them, warm them up, change them. I mean, that\'s all very standard stuff, but if I was really going to do this whole'

[27:15] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Lightroom path and bother with that, of course, I would probably just take a dedicated purpose-built Micro Four Thirds camera, which will give me far more capability than this does. So, as a camera reviewer, I love playing with quirky, interesting stuff. Yeah, I like'

[27:28] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'I mean, it\'s neat to see what different approaches are, what different companies are trying to do. But, I am kind of left struggling with who this camera\'s for and where its uses are. So, I kind of want to just talk'

