VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'through that. Bear with me because it\'s going to get a little bit muddled, but trying to decide who this camera\'s for. Well, first, I think we can eliminate serious photographers, and that\'s fine. I mean, that was never the purpose of this camera at all. But, if you\'re a'

[27:53] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
